title: F1 - Formula 1 - 2014 Russia - Practice 1
description:
F1 - Formula 1 - 2014 Russia - Practice 1


BBC 2
Friday, October 10th, 2014




Lee McKenzie introduces coverage of the opening practice session for the Russian Grand Prix in Sochi. It is the first time in Formula 1 history that a race has been held in Russia.
